        {
            "id": 6133421,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 連貫(COHR-US)大跌5.05%，報90.39美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>連貫(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:COHR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/COHR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">COHR-US</a>)截至台北時間29日22:54股價下跌4.81美元，報90.39美元，跌幅5.05%，成交量974,307（股），盤中最高價94.19美元、最低價90.36美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.45%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.81%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-1.31%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-3.1%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>連貫(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:COHR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/COHR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">COHR-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+9.93%</li> <li>近 1 月：-8.72%</li> <li>近 3 月：+21.66%</li> <li>近 6 月：+26.61%</li> <li>今年以來：+0.5%</li></ul></section></main>",
